<h2 class="bold font-l">Lady Tremaine</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Lady Tremaine is Cinderella's abusive stepmother and is the antagonist of the story. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigBad" class='trope-example-link'>Big Bad</a></p>
</div>
</div>
